  250. abstract def allInstances[T <: UMLElement[Uml]](metaclassType: scala.reflect.api.JavaUniverse.Type, metaclass2umlOTI: scala.reflect.api.JavaUniverse.MethodSymbol, umlOTIType: scala.reflect.api.JavaUniverse.Type, scope: Option[UMLElement[Uml]])(implicit umlTag: scala.reflect.api.JavaUniverse.TypeTag[Uml], typ: scala.reflect.api.JavaUniverse.TypeTag[T]): Option[Set[T]]

    Abstract method to be implemented in a tool-specific OTI adapter.

    Abstract method to be implemented in a tool-specific OTI adapter.

    T

    The OTI UML metaclass adapter type that is the OTI adapter for the tool-specific metaclassType

    metaclassType

    The Scala runtime reflection type information about a tool-specific UML metaclass

    metaclass2umlOTI

    The Scala runtime reflection method information about the OTI adapter for converting an instance of a tool-specific UML metaclasse to the corresponding tool-specific OTI UML adapter instance

    umlOTIType

    The Scala runtime reflection type information about a tool-specific OTI UML metaclass adapter

    scope

    An OTI UML element scoping the result of the instances of the OTI UML metaclasses to look for, or None for a global query

    umlTag

    The Scala type information about the OTI UML adaptation trait: Uml

    typ

    The Scala type information about the OTI UML metaclass adapter

    returns

    The OTI UML metaclass adapter instances to look for globally or within the ownership scope of some element

  500. def allInstances[T <: UMLElement[Uml]](metaclassName: String, scope: Option[UMLElement[Uml]])(implicit umlTag: scala.reflect.api.JavaUniverse.TypeTag[Uml], typ: scala.reflect.api.JavaUniverse.TypeTag[T], opsTag: scala.reflect.api.JavaUniverse.TypeTag[UMLOps[Uml]]): Option[Set[T]]

    Functionally equivalent to the following OCL query: <metaclass>.allInstances()->select(e | scope <> null implies e->closure(owner)->union(e)->includes(scope))

    Functionally equivalent to the following OCL query: <metaclass>.allInstances()->select(e | scope <> null implies e->closure(owner)->union(e)->includes(scope))

    T

    The OTI UML metaclass adapter corresponding to the OMG UML metaclass name

    metaclassName

    The name of an OMG UML metaclass

    scope

    An OTI UML element scoping the result of the instances of the OTI UML metaclasses to look for, or None for a global query

    umlTag

    The Scala type information about the OTI UML adaptation trait: Uml

    typ

    The Scala type information about the OTI UML metaclass adapter

    opsTag

    The Scala type information about the OTI UML Operations type

    returns

    The OTI UML metaclass adapter instances to look for globally or within the ownership scope of some element
